results.title: The Mark
results.description: As Bauer prepares for an assault by Elektra, Prebble tells him of his adventures being stalked by the ninja assassin.

results.title: The Job
results.description: Story rewinds and illustrates Mr. Prebble's bloody history with Elektra as told to Bauer last issue.

results.title: Power Play
results.description: Elektra is on the trail of a ruthless African dictator and her lecherous son.

results.title: Power Play Part 2
results.description: Story backtracks and explains how Elektra snuck into an African country to attempt to take down its ruthless dictator and her son.

results.title: Power Play Part 3
results.description: Elektra not only takes down the evil dictator she was commissioned to kill but also settles the score with the guy who tried to rip her off in hiring her for the mission.

results.title: [Ninja Time]
results.description: Hydra asks Elektra to complete the same mission Shield gave her but for Hydra instead; When she refuses, they sic the Silver Samurai on her.

results.title: [Total Media Blackout]
results.description: While Elektra fights the Samurai, Saddam prepares to use the Scorpio Key.

results.title: [Game Bloody Over]
results.description: Elektra obtains the Scorpio Key, snubs both Hydra and Shield and gives it to the unlikeliest of people.

results.title: [Nuff Said]
results.description: Elektra foils an assassination attempt on Matt Murdock's life.

results.title: [Untitled]
results.description: A mysterious woman uses an Interpol agent to contact Elektra for a job; Elektra is asked to bring in four men who raped Katamides ten years ago.

results.title: [Untitled]
results.description: Elektra delivers the four rapists to Katamides.

results.title: [Untitled]
results.description: Elektra refuses to help Katamides have her sadistic revenge on the men who raped her.

results.title: Planet Earth is No More!
results.description: Strange enters Dimension of Dreams, defeats Nightmare, & releases Eternity.  Nightmare had caused Eternity to dream the end of the Earth.  The Ancient One intervenes, & Eternity recreates Earth.

results.title: Cover #43044
results.description: Cover text: The Sorcerer Supreme battles alone against an unholy host in...the Devil's workshop!

results.title: Where There's Smoke...
results.description: James Mandarin desperately slits own throat at Strange's doorstep; wants Strange to be his guru, but is rejected. Strange tells of recreation of Earth to Lord Phyffe, Rama Kaliph, & Clea. Clea freaks. Mandarin is possessed by Satan, & Satan abducts them.

results.title: Cover #43046
results.description: To save the woman he loves, the Sorcerer Supreme must voyage to the L& Beyond the Living!  Trapped between the Devil & the Dead

results.title: Beelzebub on Parade!
results.description: Strange battles Satan in Hell.  Lord Phyffe & Rama Kaliph perform exorcism, which gives Strange stability to overcome Satan's lies.

results.title: Cover #43048
results.description: Strange & Clea in Stygyro's time trap

results.title: Utopia Rising!
results.description: M&arin attempts to steal magic books, including New Atlantis by Sir Francis Bacon.  Strange & Clea travel back in time to trace origins of America.  They hobnob with Bacon.  Stygyro, Prince of Sorcerers, attacks Strange.

results.title: Cover #43050
results.description: This Dream No More!  Strange battles a Serpent with Clea clinging to his leg.

results.title: The Dream is Dead!
results.description: Strange & Clea continue their time travel & meet Benjamin Franklin.  Franklin & Clea have amorous encounter.  Stygyro attacks again in form of sea serpent, in the ruins of Atlantis.

results.title: Cover #43052
results.description: Sorcerer No More!  Strange attacked by skeletons, including Clea.

results.title: Lo, the Powers Changeth!
results.description: X&er & Creators reveal plans to destroy universe. Stygyro attacks again, causing an earthquake. Strange reverses time & undoes damage. Strange rejects oneness w/universe offered by Ancent One & is stripped of Sorcerer Supreme powers.

results.title: Call Him: Xander the Merciless!
results.description: Strange battles Xander the Merciless.  Xander erases Clea's memory; she goes on magical rampage. Xander reveals that Creators planted idea in Ancient One's mind of testing Strange for ultimate life conversion; resulted in stripping of Strange's powers.

results.title: The most shocking story of all!  Sorcerer against the woman he loves!
"The Coming of... Dr. Strange"
results.description: Origin of Dr. Strange

results.title: Mind Trip!
results.description: Clea's amnesia & magical rampage continues.  Strange battles Clea, & helps cure her of madness implanted by Xander.  Apalla, Queen of the Sun, first appears; hints of connection with Clea.

results.title: Into the Quadriverse!
results.description: Strange enters the Quadriverse, & saves the female Guardian.  He is unknowingly infected by little demon.

results.title: The Master of the Mystic Arts teams with the mysterious Apalla to battle--The Creators!  What price the Universe?
A Change Cometh!
results.description: The Creators are using Cosmic Wheel of Change to form new universe, with themselves as Gods/Stars. Strange enters Quadriverse, & battles Visimajoris, the Soul Divider.  Apalla, Queen of the Sun, joins battle.  Strange goofs & wrecks Wheel of Change.
